snippet.title: Sky Climb | Launch Trailer | Available now on Meta Quest!
snippet.description:
🌤️ Get Sky Climb NOW on Meta Store: https://www.meta.com/experiences/6439300372853604/

The Ultimate Virtual Reality Platformer Game of Dynamic Adventures across Captivating Worlds 🪽

Explore an Exhilarating 65-Levels Singleplayer Campaign, a 6-Players Thrilling Multiplayer action-packed Championship and an Innovative Level Builder ☀️

Sky Climb is the game that will take your Virtual Reality gaming experience to new heights. Get ready to soar through the skies and embrace the thrill of platforming like never before! ☁️
